comments: Eubanks (PHX) causes marginal contact to occur with Vucevic (CHI) as they engage during Vucevic's dribble in the post.
Allen (PHX) and Williams (CHI) mutually engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Durant (PHX) takes more than eight seconds to establish the ball in the frontcourt.
Allen (PHX) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Beal (PHX) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path during the pick, and marginal contact occurs as Beal releases to roll to the basket.
Beal (PHX) brings both hands to the ball and deflects it away from Vucevic (CHI) before incidental contact occurs during the rebound.
Vucevic (CHI) and Nurkic (PHX) engage off-ball before the screen is set, and the contact is marginal.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul on Durant (PHX).
Nurkic (PHX) is establishing himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Caruso (CHI) trails behind to contest and avoids making contact with Durant (PHX) during his jump shot attempt.

Bates-Diop (PHX) initiates illegal body contact with Williams (CHI) as he attempts to get to the pass. The contact occurs before Williams touches the ball, and the clock is correctly reset to 00:01.6.
Allen (PHX) and DeRozan (CHI) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
As Williams (CHI) attempts to slip to the basket, marginal body contact occurs with Allen (PHX), which does not affect his ability to maintain his defensive positioning.
Williams' (CHI) right foot is out of bounds when he illegally screens Nurkic (PHX).
Durant (PHX) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
